<a name="event5"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3>New Activist Orientation</h4>
  <h4>Saturday, November 4th</h4>
  <h4>TBA</h4>
  <p>Ever wanted to be an activist but too nervous to show up unprepared? Worried about what's legal and what rights you have? Unsure how non-violence as a tactic can drive social change? Want to meet other local people interested in activism? This day is for you! More details to come soon!<p>
  <a href="mailto:Mansibhagwate@gmail.com?Subject=RSVP%20for%20Activisty%20Orientation" target="_blank">RSVP</a>
</div>

<a name="event1"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3>Weekly Planning Meetings</h4>
  <h4>Every Monday Night</h4>
  <h4>6:30 pm - 9:00 pm</h4>
  <p>Join us every Monday night at Uptwinkles for dinner and our planning meeting. Meetings are open to anyone who is interested in getting more involved with organizing for Liberation Philly, has input to share on a particular topic to be discussed, or is generally curious about how we work.</p>
  <p>Please let Mary Kate know if you plan to attend, so we can account for you in the dinner plan!<p>
  <a href="mailto:mkfain@gmail.com?Subject=RSVP%20for%20Weekly%20Meeting" target="_blank">RSVP</a>
</div>

<a name="event3"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3>Sanctuary Volunteer Day</h4>
  <h4>Sunday, October 15th</h4>
  <h4>9:00 am - 5:00 pm</h4>
  <p>Get your hands dirty helping animals! Hop on board the caravan to Tamerlain Farm Sanctuary, a safe-haven for individuals rescued from the industries of abuse and exploitation. Cuddle with pigs, play with chickens, and get inspired by their stories.</p>
  <p>RSVP to Mansi to reserve a spot!<p>
  <a href="mailto:Mansibhagwate@gmail.com?Subject=RSVP%20for%20Sanctuary%20Day" target="_blank">RSVP</a>
</div>

<a name="event2"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3>Monthly Day of Action</h4>
  <h4>Saturday, October 28th</h4>
  <h4>1:00 pm - 3:00 pm</h4>
  <p>Take action for animals! Join Liberation Philly in our monthly day of action, a non-violent protest aimed at raising public discourse around animal rights. Please arive at Uptinkles at 1:00 pm to review the action plan and non-violence prior to the action, as well as to meet new activists.</p>
  <p>RSVPs are helpful in planning, but not mandatory. Bring a friend!<p>
  <a href="mailto:mkfain@gmail.com?Subject=RSVP%20for%October%20DoA" target="_blank">RSVP</a>
</div>

<a name="event4"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3>Philly Farmed Animal Save - Vigil</h4>
  <h4>Sunday, November 18th</h4>
  <h4>TBA</h4>
  <p>Join us in bearing witness and paying respect to just a few of the billions of lives losts. The first Save Movement vigil in Philly we be hosts at a local slaughterhouse, signs and candles will be provided. Please wear black if possible. The event location will be released shortly before the event.</p>
  <p>RSVP to get event updates.<p>
  <a href="mailto:mkfain@gmail.com?Subject=RSVP%20for%November%20Vigil" target="_blank">RSVP</a></div>
</div>

